      • divideIntoClassPropertyInstance

        public static Map<EvaluatorUtil.ConfusionMatrixType,ExecutionResult> divideIntoClassPropertyInstance(ExecutionResult executionResult)
        Divides an execution result into multiple execution results according to the type of the objects (classes, properties, instances). This operation can be used, to calculate metrics on a fine-granular level, for instance.
        Parameters:
        executionResult - Execution result that shall be divided into classes, properties, and instances
        Returns:
        A Map of form EvaluatorUtil.ConfusionMatrixType to ExecutionResult where the execution results contain only a subset of the data according to the type.
